# Backend Conventions

## File Structure

- `src/index.ts` - Express server, all REST endpoints
- `src/auth.ts` - SIWE nonce generation, verification, HMAC session tokens
- `src/db.ts` - SQLite via better-sqlite3 (users, agents tables)
- `src/eigencompute.ts` - `ecloud` CLI wrapper for TEE deployment

## API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Auth | Purpose |
|--------|------|------|---------|
| GET | `/api/auth/nonce` | No | Generate SIWE nonce (5min TTL) |
| POST | `/api/auth/verify` | No | Verify SIWE, return session token |
| POST | `/api/agents/deploy` | Yes | Deploy agent to EigenCompute |
| GET | `/api/agents/info` | Yes | Get user's agent status |
| POST | `/api/agents/stop` | Yes | Stop agent container |
| POST | `/api/agents/start` | Yes | Start stopped agent |
| POST | `/api/agents/terminate` | Yes | Remove agent permanently |
| POST | `/api/agents/task` | Yes | Proxy task to agent |
| GET | `/api/agents/skills` | Yes | Proxy skill list from agent |
| GET | `/api/agents/history` | Yes | Proxy audit log from agent |

## Auth Pattern

```typescript
// Session token format: address:expiresAt:hmac
// HMAC = sha256(address:expiresAt, TOKEN_SECRET)
// Timing-safe comparison for verification
```

## Key Patterns

- **One agent per user**: Check `db.getAgent(userAddress)` before deploy
- **Mnemonic injection**: Generate via `@scure/bip39`, pass to ecloud as env var, never store
- **Rate limiting**: Auth endpoints 10/min, deploy 10/hour
- **Zod validation**: All request bodies validated with schemas
- **ecloud name**: `clawt-${userAddress.slice(2, 10)}`

## Environment Variables

```
TOKEN_SECRET        # HMAC signing secret
FRONTEND_URL        # CORS allowed origin
EIGENCOMPUTE_EMAIL  # ecloud CLI auth
EIGENCOMPUTE_PASSWORD
DOCKER_IMAGE        # Agent image ref (clawt/agent:latest)
```
